headline: Ashcor and Consumers Energy Announce Coal Ash Remediation at J.H. Campbell Power Plant
summary: Ashcor USA Inc., a subsidiary of Ashcor Technologies Ltd. and a division of ATCO Ltd. (TSX: ACO.X) (TSX: ACO.Y), and Michigan-based Consumers Energy are excited to announce an agreement to extract and repurpose millions of tons of impounded coal ash from the soon to be retired J.H. Campbell Generating Complex.
